      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_ebf9801b75ac2bbb185d3ea25258d3d9">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The papers consist of a typescript short story by Seldes; playscripts by Richard H. Hepburn, Ira Levin, Anne Sexton, Tennessee Williams and others, some accompanied by related correspondence and photographs; and a pen and wash portrait by William Ivey Long of Seldes as Persephone in Aristophones' The Frogs.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
